              "type": "cs-basic-text",
              "settings": {
                "content": "<p>I wanted something pure and uncomplicated after years of ingredient lists I couldn't pronounce. That's exactly what I found with <strong>Pure Tallow Co.'s Organic Grass-Fed Tallow Cream<\/strong>.<\/p><p>Here's why it worked when nothing else had:<\/p><p>✓ <strong>100% Pure Ingredients<\/strong> – Just grass-fed beef tallow with optional organic essential oils. No water, preservatives, or synthetic additives.<\/p><p>✓ <strong>Biocompatible Formula<\/strong> – Contains the same fatty acids and fat-soluble vitamins that human skin naturally produces.<\/p><p>✓ <strong>Deep Penetration<\/strong> – Unlike water-based moisturizers that sit on top, tallow absorbs completely without leaving a greasy residue.<\/p><p>✓ <strong>Multi-Purpose<\/strong> – One product for face, body, hands, lips, even hair ends.<\/p><p>✓ <strong>Traditional Process<\/strong> – Rendered using centuries-old methods that preserve all beneficial compounds.<\/p>"
              }
            },
