              "type": "cs-basic-text",
              "settings": {
                "content": "<p>Let me be honest—I had tried everything. Prescription creams from dermatologists, $80 serums from luxury brands, \"clean\" beauty products that cost more than my grocery bill. Most either did nothing or made my skin worse.<\/p><p>Here's what makes Pure Tallow Co. completely different:<\/p><p>✓ <strong>No Synthetic Irritants<\/strong> – Zero parabens, sulfates, synthetic fragrances, or preservatives that can trigger sensitivity.<\/p><p>✓ <strong>Mimics Natural Sebum<\/strong> – Works with your skin's biology instead of against it.<\/p><p>✓ <strong>Long-Lasting Hydration<\/strong> – One application provides moisture for 12+ hours, unlike water-based creams that evaporate.<\/p><p>✓ <strong>Repairs Barrier Function<\/strong> – Actually helps restore your skin's natural protective barrier over time.<\/p><p>✓ <strong>Historically Proven<\/strong> – Used successfully for thousands of years across cultures worldwide.<\/p><p><strong>This isn't just another moisturizer—it's a return to what actually works.<\/strong><\/p>"
